Package me.masstrix.eternalnature.menus

Class Button

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.masstrix.eternalnature.menus.Button
  • public class Button
extends java.lang.Object
    Buttons are a more simple to use way of handling items with actions in an inventory. Being able to store a click action along with an update method it makes handling a menus icon a bit easier.
